data.name: Label6.Text
data.value:
Welcome to the Napier Archery Freshers Fair Mailing List software.
- This software gathers a user's Name and Student Number (and email if required) - The data is stored on your computer in CSV format. C:\NapierArchery - The software automatically produces a student email if the user enters a student number - The CSV file is compatible with Gmail's "import contacts" feature -- the numerous blank fields in the CSV file is normal.
HOW TO USE: 1- Enter a group name. This label will be attached to the contacts when uploaded to Gmail. This allows you to email everyone by entering just the group name. 2- Press the Initialise button. 3- Allow users to input their data 4- When finished, exit the program with Alt-Tab or Alt-F4. -- If the program is closed prematurely, just restart it. -- Additional data will be added to the end of the CSV file.
Check the Record Personal Emails box if the club is permitted to store personal emails. An extra "Personal Email" field will be added to the form.

data.name: Label7.Text
data.value: Napier Archery only uses your data to send you information about upcoming archery related events. We only keep your data for one semester, unless you request we remove it earlier. If you join Archery, your details will be kept for the duration of your membership. We will not supply this data to any third parties.
